releaseNotes:
# trtree
## Summary
Print a parse tree in a human-readable format
## Description
Reads a tree from stdin and prints the tree as an indented node list.
## Usage
trtree
## Examples
trparse A.g4 | trtree
## Current version
0.21.1 Fix to trconvert for Bison. Add trquery. Fixes to trperf, trparse.
